name: TIM CHEESE
description: Who Is $TIM Cheese? $Tim Cheese isn’t your average meme—he’s the Brainrot Supreme Leader, the meme-slaying menace your favorite TikTok skibidi toilet wishes it could be. Born in the darkest corners of the internet, this unhinged mouse with glasses has one goal: to yeet every weak meme into the void. John Pork? Gone. Marvin Beak? Obliterated. $Tim Cheese doesn’t play; he dominates. Now he’s here to flex on the blockchain with $TIMCHEESE, turning brainrot into straight-up profit. Bow down or get ratio’d, Ohio-style.
